      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it has been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it to get you where you need to go comfortably. It runs beautifully and is just waiting for a new owner to take it out on the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I do!",
