      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2006 Porsche 911 Carrera features the revered 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant benefits from VarioCam Plus variable valve timing and lift, ensuring a robust torque curve throughout the rev range. The chassis remains composed, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup that provides exceptional lateral stability and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Deceleration is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled, ventilated rotors. This example is a highly capable driver, with a drivetrain that remains tight and synchros that engage without hesitation. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with regular use, it is mechanically sorted and ready for spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
